OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780391237
OL,3,CMan appears in court after military
OL,4,Csilhouette from Ramsgate Harbour
OL,5,Cdamaged
OL,7,FA man has appeared in court after a
OL,8,Fmilitary silhouette in Ramsgate was
OL,9,Fdamaged.
OL,11,FHe was reported to have been seen with
OL,12,Fwhat appeared to be a weapon near West
OL,13,FCliff Promenade.
OL,15,FPolice were called to the scene on the
OL,16,Fevening of Friday, May 29 - and the
OL,17,Fman was arrested in connection with
OL,18,Fthe incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
