OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780391237
OL,3,CMan appears in court after military
OL,4,Csilhouette from Ramsgate Harbour
OL,5,Cdamaged
OL,7,FOfficers later established that a
OL,8,Frifle which belonged to one of the 338
OL,9,F'Standing with Giants' silhouettes had
OL,10,Fbeen snapped off.
OL,12,FThe installations are currently in
OL,13,Fplace around Ramsgate harbour until
OL,14,Fthe end of June, representing every
OL,15,F1,000 soldiers rescued from the
OL,16,Fbeaches in Dunkirk in Operation Dynamo.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
