OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1780391237
OL,3,CMan appears in court after military
OL,4,Csilhouette from Ramsgate Harbour
OL,5,Cdamaged
OL,7,FKaine McCullum, of Northdown Road,
OL,8,FCliftonville, has been charged with
OL,9,Fcriminal damage, possession of an
OL,10,Foffensive weapon in a public place,
OL,11,Fcommon assault and using threatening
OL,12,For abusive words or behaviour to cause
OL,13,Fharassment, alarm or distress.
OL,15,FThe 39-year-old appeared at Margate
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court today. He has been
OL,17,Fremanded in custody until his next
OL,18,Fcourt appearance on June 8.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
